@startuml
title Trade Domain Model

class Trade {
  +trade_id: string
  +counterparty_id: string
  +book_id: string
  +version: int
  +maturity_date: date
  +created_date: date
  +expired: bool
}

class MongoTrade <<document>> {
  _id: ObjectId
  trade_id: string
  version: int
  book_id: string
  ... (same fields)
}

class SqlTrade <<table dbo.trades>> {
  trade_id: varchar(50) <<PK>>
  version: int <<PK>>
  book_id: varchar(50) <<PK>>
  counterparty_id: varchar(50)
  maturity_date: date
  created_date: date
  expired: bit
}

Trade -> MongoTrade : mapped to document
Trade -> SqlTrade : mapped to row

@enduml
